Speech to Text: Hey doctor there is something wrong with my head can you please check it
Doctor's Response: With what I see, I think you have dandruff, a common scalp condition characterized by flakes of dead skin, and it appears to be causing some scaling on your scalp. I would suggest using an antifungal shampoo, specifically one containing ingredients such as zinc pyrithione or ketoconazole, and also recommend trying to reduce stress and using a gentle scalp massager to help loosen and remove the flakes.
